{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d25fe6d5-a462-41b9-a189-a8fac34d46fd","content":"No files found in the workspace. I'll provide the solution directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` to enable compiled bindings:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"16\">\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" Placeholder=\"Theme\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"32\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` — this tells the XAML compiler the type of the `BindingContext`, enabling compile-time resolution of all `{Binding}` paths.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **Enable strict mode** in your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n   This promotes binding warnings to **errors**, failing the build if a property name is wrong (e.g., `{Binding Themee}` won't compile).\n\n2. **Without the strict flag**, the compiler emits warnings (XC00##) for invalid paths. Run:\n   ```bash\n   dotnet build -warnaserror\n   ```\n   to treat them as errors in CI.\n\n3. **If you need to opt out** for a specific subtree (e.g., a templated control with a different context), use `x:DataType=\"\"` to disable compiled bindings locally.\n\nWith `x:DataType` in place, typos in property names, wrong types in converters, and missing properties are all caught **before** runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"642cda4c-cf5d-4547-9915-f210c34cbeaa","outputTokens":546,"requestId":"E84B:2FA1DA:24FC8CC:290220E:69F93E66"},"id":"1f9845e3-829c-4f49-8989-80d9b5195972","timestamp":"2026-05-05T00:48:49.898Z","parentId":"226ed612-95a3-4ffc-84c5-9dd8b901bb71"}
